Returns an {{rlp|iterator}} or a {{rlp|sentinel}} that compares equal to the end iterator of the {{rlpt|/|zip_transform_view}}.

Let {{tt|zip_}} denote the underlying tuple of views:

@1@ Equivalent to: &lt;br&gt;{{c|
if constexpr (ranges::common_range&lt;/*InnerView*/&gt;)
    return /*iterator*/&lt;false&gt;(*this, zip_.end());
else
    return /*sentinel*/&lt;false&gt;(zip_.end());
}}

@2@ Equivalent to: &lt;br&gt;{{c|
if constexpr (ranges::common_range&lt;const /*InnerView*/&gt;)
    return /*iterator*/&lt;true&gt;(*this, zip_.end());
else
    return /*sentinel*/&lt;true&gt;(zip_.end());
}}

===Parameters===
(none)

===Return value===
An iterator or sentinel representing the end of the {{tt|zip_transform_view}}, as described above.
